## Grattari Classes
Below are the Class changes when playing within the world of Grattum.



{{classTable,frame,decoration,wide
##### Classes
|Class|Description|Hit Die|Primary Ability|Saving Throw Proficiencies|Armor and Weapon Proficiencies|
|:---|:---|:---:|:---:|:---|:---|
|Wildkin| Barbarian Druid esque combo. Unarmed/Fist weapon class that utilizes totems and disease curses to weaken enemies | d12 | Strength & Wisdom | Strength & Constitution | TBD |
|Cyberbeast| Cyber druid, think bio transformer. Can utilize different aspects to transform or enhance spells | d8 | Dexterity & Wisdom | Wisdom & Strength | TBD |
|Malechite| Gem warrior, where gemstone is graphed to your body to enhance you | d10 | Strength & Dexterity | Constitution & Wisdom | TBD |
|Synth| Synthetic enhancements, i.e. cyberpunk 2077. Ranger/Rogue double up. Each Enhancement has benifits of infiltrator or manipulator | d8 | Dexterity | Dexterity & Intelligence | TBD |
|Harnesser| Wizard in grattum. Can harness the power of the Weave and Astral Spheres. Can manipulate life, death, space, time, and anything else the weave touches | d8 | Intelligence | Intelligence & Charisma | TBD |
|Planetspeaker| pseduo religious fenatic that interacts with the celestial bodies of import. Gains special spell and abilites based on which celesital body they communne with | d10 | Dexterity & Charisma | Wisdom & Constitution | TBD |
|Artificer| Masters of invention, artificers use ingenuity and magic to unlock extraordinary capabilities in objects.  | d8 | Intelligence | Constitution & Intelligence | Light armor, medium armor, shields, Simple Weapons | 

