## Class Features
- Druid - Cyberbeast
  - Subclass Name: Aspect
    - Aspect of Gaia
    - Aspect of Sil'me
    - Aspect of Fal'de
    - Aspect of Rakk'se
    
## Celestial Aspect
Cyberbeasts are allows to transform and enhance their abilites once they commune with a celestial aspect. this can be the very planet they walk on, either of the great moons, or even the sun.

### Aspect of Gaia
Grants Eternium shapes. Eternium shapes are resistant to all damage. Immune to non-magical damage.All attacks while shifted, are magical and immune to resistance. spells are more potent and deal more damage.

### Aspect of Sil'me
Grants undead shapes. Dead variant for shapes, all attack while shifted are necrotic and reduce max HP. Spells cannot heal, only harm.

### Aspect of Fal'de
Grants Plant shapes. While plant shaped, all attacks and spells heal allies for more and you can prevent disease, death, and other harm. All spells have a healing component attached to them now as well.

### Aspect of Rakk'se
Grants Fire Shapes. while shifted, all attacks deal fire damage. cannot be resisted and burns continually for exponential damage. all spells shift to unresistable fire damage. any allies caught in fire are instead healed.
