## Gemstone Graft
Grafting the power of gemstones to your body grants extra power

### Resilience of Ruby
More Max HP, recieves better healing, can enhance weaponry with fire.

### Grace of Emerald
Can stave off attacks and deflect the ones that hit. Increased movement speed and attack speed. can enhance weaponry with acid

### Wisdom of Amethyst
Increases spell power, can cast some spells, find weak points on enemies and exploit them. can enhance weaponry with poision

### Edurance of Eternium
Immune to exhaustion, Immune to max heal reduction, Unstoppable, attacks deal extra damage, can enhance weaponry with Bleed, Disease, and Curses
