     Use --rotation to set rotation angle in degrees. -->
### The Burnwood
Nearly thirty years ago **The Fracture** introducted many changes to the natural order of the world. One of the more notable ones, was **The Burnwood**, a northern forest of The Lands Abound, changed by an ancient Fae Curse. The *Solstice Curse* forced the land to be put into a perptual autumn, with many of the wildlife changing accordingly. 

Most native creatures fled the Burnwood, with new Fae denizens taking their place. Where the Blackwald houses the dark forces of the Fae, the Burnwood in turn houses the more mischievous and mild Fae Folk. With the main path leading away from Farendell flowing through the Burnwood, many travelers and adventurers alike prefer this "scenic" route through the Lands. While the main road proves safe for many, venturing off the beaten path may lead to memorable encounters of all sort.

### The Scorched Scar
Although **The Burnwood** may prove safe for many travelers, all must pass through **The Scorched Scar**, a barren land that streches through the Burnwood all the way to **The Ashen Forest**. Only a few short years following The Fracture, an undead dragon infused with Fae, Shadowfell, and Dark Magic rose within the south of the Burnwood; **A Necrodrake**. 

This Necrodrake's flame cauterized the life force of the land it touched, ceasing all ability to thrive, and raising any life it took. All along the Scar, undead now walk and kill all living things. Only the main road holds some small safety, as guardsmen and fame seekers drift along the road to protect the commonfolk, and passing adventurers. 

It was only 5 years ago, a brave band of adventureres rose up to defeat the Necrodrake, ultimately sacraficing their lives to pull it from the sky and destroy it once and for all. But, as the force behind the Necrodrake's undeath wavered and ultimately extingushed, its remains tainted the land it was felled in. Eventually, it's unholy remains created the desecrated land known as **The Ashen Forest**



\page
{{pageNumber,auto}}

{{imageMaskCorner32,--offsetX:-65%,--offsetY:50%,--rotation:0
  ![](https://github.com/PhantomDesk74/Homebrewery_Assets/blob/main/BookArt/Ashen%20Forest.png?raw=true){height:100%,transform:scaleX(-1)}
