{{wide
# The Prime Deities
The Prime Deities rule above all others. There are none who govern the Primes, only the Primes rule, and amongst the Prime, none are above. Although the denizens of Rakktenn primarily worship the Primes, other gods have found their footholds of power. The Greater Deities directly fall under the domains of the Prime, and beneath the Greater Deities are more Lesser gods that hold a modicom of power. While this list includes many gods and otherworldly beings, consult your DM to see where your god of choice may fall in the divine ordering.
}}
{{wide,column-count:2
### Ultera
#### The Omega
:
##### Alignment {{width:100px}}  Domains
###### Lawful  {{width:120px}} Arcana, Order,</br>{{width:150px}} Knowledge, Twilight
::
Ultera is the First. The Omega. Through her, all stories are told, all destinies, Woven.

Ultera stands above Law, Above Chaos. She will do what is written, what is always meant to be. Her Weavesown walk the plains to keep Order and Design in all corners of the Multiverse. To be chosen by Ultra is to be chosen by The One Above All.

Your Destiny will be Fractured, as you will traverse the Fabric of Reality, to sew the threads of fate together.
:

The Holy Symbol of Ultera is **<u>The Omega.</u>**
