As the first Goddess, she is the bringer of all things, allowing the beauty of creation to flurish from the Chaos of the Darkness.

**Timera's Children**, as her followers call themselves, seek to bring a lasting peace to the world through the encouragement of kindess and love, through a gentle guiding hand.
