### Lonard
#### The Lord of Storms
:
##### Alignment {{width:100px}}  Domains
###### Lawful Good {{width:70px}} Twilight, Tempest, Nature

:
The Youngest of the Prime, and the only known God to ascend as first a mortal, Lonard is the embodiment of a true Warrior. Whilst his followers share his brash nature and quick action, many see Lonard as a beacon to what any mortal can strive to be. The thought that any man, woman, or child can have the conviction to be ascended, has led many to search for a "greater purpose". 

The **The Lord of Storms** is a being that not many trifle with, and even less with his followers. Those who worship Lonard belong to many Paladin Orders, Tribesmen of the Wilds, and even some Clergy.
:
The Holy Symbol of Londard is a <u>**Thundercloud Pierced by a Longsword wrapped in Lightning.**</u>
