|  4th  |  +2  | Ability Score Increase  | 3 | 5 | 2 | 2nd |
|  5th  |  +3  |  - | 3 | 6 | 2 | 3rd |
|  6th  |  +3  |  Soulless  | 3 | 7 | 2 | 3rd |
