| 11th  |  +4  | Bound by Blood   | 4 | 11 | 3 | 6th |
| 12th  |  +4  | Ability Score Increase | 4 | 11 | 3 | 6th |
| 13th  |  +5  | Tainted Knowledge  | 4 | 12 | 3 | 7th |
