| 19th  | +6 | Ability Score Improvement |    4     | 4  | 3  | 3  | 3  | 2  | 2  | 1  | 1  | 1  |
| 20th  | +6 | Angel of Eternity |    4     | 4  | 3  | 3  | 3  | 2  | 2  | 2  | 1  | 1  |
