}}
#### Speed
Your base walking speed is 25 feet. Your speed is not reduced by wearing heavy armor.

#### Ability Score Increase
Your Strength score increases by 2.
Your Consitution score increases by 1.


#### Dwarven Armor Training
You have proficiency with light and medium armor.

#### Savage Nature
The Slayer's Mark gives you an unquenchable thirst for battle. You gain the **Savage Attacker** Feat.

#### Gift of Malice
Joining the Slayer Sect grants you a Slayer weapon. This weapon can be any weapon of your choice, but mechanically funtions with the following traits

##### Slayer Weapon
