{{wide,text-align:center
# Mythical Feats
}}
{{pageNumber,auto}}
{{wide
Mythical Feats are the pinnicale of power within Fal'Doren. Normal feats allow for expanded prowess in class archetypes, but Mythical Feats allow for additonal Story Elements, Class Enhancment, or even allowing new and interesting takes on downtime features.
:
All of these feats can only be obtained via award through the DM's discretion. These are not meant to be easily obtained, but meant to enhance the natural progression of your Character Archs.
}}

<!--
