{{monster,frame
## Marvin Trailis
*Medium Shifter (Weretiger), Chaotic Neutral Ranger* - *Arcanite*
___
**Armor Class** :: 15 (leather armor)
**Hit Points** :: 26 (4d8 + 8)
**Speed** :: 30 ft.
___
|STR|DEX|CON|INT|WIS|CHA|
|:---:|:---:|:---:|:---:|:---:|:---:|
|8 (-1)|18 (+4)|14 (+2)|12 (+1)|14 (+2)|11 (+0)|
___
**Saving Throws** :: Str +1, Dex +6
**Skills** :: Acrobatics +6, Athletics +1, Intimidation +2, Nature +3, Stealth +6, Survival +4
**Senses** :: darkvision 60 ft., passive Perception 12
**Languages** :: Common, Draconic
**Challenge** :: 4 (1,100 XP)
___
Marvin is an egotistical ranger who specializes in getting himself in trouble. While Sly and Cunning may be his dominant traits, anyone can tell he has a deep respect and care for his party members.

Marvin is usually dressed in various leathers, sporting a dark, forest-green cloak. He regularly will have a half smoked cigarette dangling from his mouth, while playing with is many knives set within his brandolere across his chest.

}}


{{monster,frame
## Brutus Grantium
*Medium Dwarf, Neutral Good Fighter* - *Arcanite*
___
**Armor Class** :: 16 (chain mail)
**Hit Points** :: 30 (4d8 + 12)
**Speed** :: 25 ft.
___
