**Languages** :: Common, Dwarvish, Giant
**Challenge** :: 4 (1,100 XP)
___
Brutus is the personification of Dwarven values, but make no mistake, he'll treat you like family until the end. Wise beyond his years, Brtus is a brutal fighter, looking to make sure his enemies can't harm any close to him.

Brutus wears a large chain shirt and wields two hand axes, ready to strike at a moments notice. The rest of his clothes are ragged and worn, with seemingly little care taken to their upkeep.
