{{monster,frame

## Natalia Heurmon
*Medium Human, Lawful Neutral Paladin* - *Arcanite*
___
**Armor Class** :: 18 (chain mail, shield)
**Hit Points** :: 26 (4d8 + 8)
**Speed** :: 30 ft.
___
|STR|DEX|CON|INT|WIS|CHA|
|:---:|:---:|:---:|:---:|:---:|:---:|
|16 (+3)|14 (+2)|14 (+2)|11 (+0)|9 (-1)|16 (+3)|
