Sylvia Barrowmere is a skilled Arcanite Mage who specalizes in protecting her allies and countering her foes. As one of the prominent  **Escort Class** Arcanites, she regularly finds herself on the *Gold Road*, the path leading to the small town of Firemorn, originating from the *Arcane Citadel.*

Plenty of fledgling Arcanites know of Sylvia and all recounts of adventures including her have been filled with a plethora of compliments and commendations.
