{{monster,frame
## Grimia
*Medium Shifter, Neutral Merchant*
___
**Armor Class** :: 11 (14 with mage armor)
**Hit Points** :: 22 (4d8 + 4)
**Speed** :: 40 ft.
___
|STR|DEX|CON|INT|WIS|CHA|
|:---:|:---:|:---:|:---:|:---:|:---:|
|10 (+0)|12 (+1)|12 (+1)|16 (+3)|18 (+4)|16 (+3)|
