**Senses** :: darkvision 60 ft., passive Perception 14
**Languages** :: Common, Elvish, Sylvan
**Challenge** :: 4 (1,100 XP)
___
Grimia is a trader who sells a variety of magical items, scrolls, and custom healing potions that are uniquely "Made to Order." She is usually more interested in the characters that visit her shop and their adventures, than making any coin from them. 

While *common* is her second language she speaks with a unique candor and takes unnatural pauses, often almost trying to find the correct words. She can usually be found in any major city that has a nature district, posting up her shop within the base of a large **Ancient**. She is fond of returning customers, especially if they have more interesting stories to tell.
}}
{{monster,frame
## Tortmund
*Medium Human, Neutral Good Trader*
___
**Armor Class** :: 15 (Mage Armor)
**Hit Points** :: 62 (10d6 + 20)
**Speed** :: 30 ft.
___
|STR|DEX|COM|INT|WIS|CHA|
|:-:|:-:|:-:|:-:|:-:|:-:|
|11 (+0)|14 (+2)|14 (+2)|18 (+4)|16 (+3)|15 (+2)|
