**Senses** :: passive Perception 17
**Languages** :: Common, Elvish, Dwarvish
**Challenge** :: 10 (5,900 XP)
___
Tortmund is the primary trader of the acclaimed Arcane Citadel. His route takes him down the *Gold Road* heading towards the small town of Firemorn to trade wares and tarrifs of the town with the goods of the citadel. 

Usually Tortmund will be accompanied by a few fledgling Arcanites that are looking to complete their training or get their feet wet in some "real" adventuring. Due to this unique partnership, The *Gold Road* and Firemorn are *usually* considered some of the "safer" roads and towns in the Northlands.
}}
