{{monster,frame,wide
## Myrrlak The Devout
*Medium dragon, Lawful Evil*
___
**Armor Class** :: 18 (Mage Armor)
**Hit Points** :: 110 (13d8 + 52)
**Speed** :: 30 ft., fly 60 ft.
___
|STR|DEX|CON|INT|WIS|CHA|
|:---:|:---:|:---:|:---:|:---:|:---:|
|14 (+2)|16 (+3)|18 (+4)|28 (+9)|19 (+4)|23 (+6)|
___
**Saving Throws** :: Int +14, Cha +11
**Skills** :: Arcana +19, Investigation +19, Sleight of Hand +8, Stealth +8
**Damage Resistances** :: Force, Psychic
**Damage Immunities** :: Cold, bludgeoning, piercing, and slashing from nonmagical attacks
**Condition Immunities** :: Charmed, Fear
**Senses** :: darkvision 120 ft., truesight 10 ft., passive Perception 14
**Languages** :: Abyssal, Draconic, Dwarvish, Primordial, Undercommon
**Challenge** :: 13 (10,000 XP)
___
### Traits
***Mighty Mind.***
Myrrlak The Devout has an unparrelled mind. Knowledge is power, and Myrrlak has gained the power of **Wall of Protection.** It can be used 14 Times before Myrrlak must take a long rest.
:
***Legendary Resistance (3/day).*** If Myrrlak The Devout fails a saving throw, it can choose to succeed instead.
:
***Spellcasting.*** Myrrlak The Devout is a 7th-level spellcaster. Its spellcasting ability is Intelligence (spell save DC 22, +14 to hit with spell attacks). The Myrrlak The Devout has the following 22 spells prepared:<br>
<br>
Cantrips (at will): _Firebolt, Frostbite, Mage Hand, True Strike, Sapping Sting_<br>
1st level (4 slots): _Mage Armor, Magic Missile, Ray of Sickness, Ice Knife, Silvery Barbs, Frost Fingers_<br>
2nd level (3 slots): _Arcane Lock, Crown of Madness, Darkness, Hold Person, Mirror Image_<br>
3rd level (3 slots): _Bestow Curse, Counterspell, Intellect Fortress, Sleet Storm_<br>
4th level (3 slots): _Banishment, Confusion, Vitriolic Sphere_<br>
5th level (2 slots): _Infernal Calling, Destructive Wave_<br>
6th level (1 slot): _Investiture of Ice_<br>
7th level (1 slot): _Finger of Death_

### Actions
***Wall of Protection***
**Casting Time:** :: 1 reaction
**Range:**        :: 15ft radius / 30ft Line centered on yourself
**Components:**   :: S
**Duration:**     :: 1 round

All allies in a 15ft radius or 30ft line horizontal to you gain a +3 to AC until the start of your next turn.
}}
