{{monster,frame,wide
## Rennak The Loyal
*Large Fiend (dragonoid), Lawful Evil*
___
**Armor Class** :: 25 (Hell Plate)
**Hit Points** :: 126 (12d10 + 60)
**Speed** :: 30 ft., fly 60 ft.
___
|STR|DEX|CON|INT|WIS|CHA|
|:---:|:---:|:---:|:---:|:---:|:---:|
|24 (+7)|18 (+4)|20 (+5)|15 (+2)|12 (+1)|22 (+6)|
___
**Saving Throws** :: Wis +5, Cha +10
**Damage Resistances** :: Necrotic, Psychic
**Damage Immunities** :: Fire
**Senses** :: blindsight 10 ft., darkvision 60 ft., passive Perception 11
**Languages** :: Draconic, understands Common
**Challenge** :: 12 (8,400 XP)
___



### Traits
***Templar's Verdict (Channel Divinity).*** For 1 minute, you gain a number of Divine Smite charges equal to your Charisma bonus. When you use Divine Smite in this way, treat all creatures as if they were undead. Additionally, you cannot roll lower than half the value of your Divine Smite damage die.
:
***Hell Plate.*** Rennak's Hell Plate protects him from all flame. Any Fire Damage taken by Rennak instead returns to him as healing.
:
***Spellcasting.*** Rennak The Loyal is a 3rd-level spellcaster. His spellcasting ability is Charisma (spell save DC 18, +10 to hit with spell attacks). Rennak The Loyal has the following 12 spells prepared:<br>
<br>
1st level (4 slots): _Compelled Duel, Command, Armor of Agathys, Wrathful Smite_<br>
2nd level (3 slots): _Locate Object, Branding Smite, Hold Person, Spiritual Weapon, Magic Weapon_<br>
3rd level (2 slots): _Blinding Smite, Spirit Shroud_
:

***Legendary Resistance (3/day).*** If Rennak The Loyal fails a saving throw, it can choose to succeed instead.
:
#### Channel Divinity.

**Conquering Presence.** You can use your Channel Divinity to exude a terrifying presence. As an action, you force each creature of your choice that you can see within 30 feet of you to make a Wisdom saving throw. On a failed save, a creature becomes frightened of you for 1 minute. The frightened creature can repeat this saving throw at the end of each of its turns, ending the effect on itself on a success.
:
**Guided Strike.** You can use your Channel Divinity to strike with supernatural accuracy. When you make an attack roll, you can use your Channel Divinity to gain a +10 bonus to the roll. You make this choice after you see the roll, but before the DM says whether the attack hits or misses.
:
### Actions
***Multiattack.*** Rennak The Loyal makes three attacks. 1 with his **Hell Claws**, 1 with his **Wicked Blade** and 1 with his **Tail Pierce**.
:
***Tail Pierce.*** _Melee Attack:_ +11 to hit, reach 10 ft., one target. _Hit:_ 14 (2d6 + 7) piercing damage.
:
***Hell Claws.*** _Melee Attack:_ +11 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. _Hit:_ 14 (2d6 + 7) slashing damage + 9 (1d4 + 7) fire damage.
:
***Wicked Blade.*** Melee Weapon Attack: +11 to hit, reach 10 ft., one target. Hit: 14 (2d6 + 7) Slashing damage. If this weapon hits, the target must make a DC 15 Dexterity saving throw taking 27 (6d8) Hellflame damage on a failed save, or half as much on a success. Hellflame damage cannot be mitigated by any means.
:
***Breath Weapon (Recharge 4-6).*** Rennak The Loyal exhales fire in a 25-foot cone. Each creature in that area must make a DC 17 Dexterity saving throw, taking 14 (4d6) fire damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one.
:

### Legendary Actions
Rennak the Loyal can take 3 legendary actions, choosing from the options below. Only one legendary action option can be used at a time and only at the end of another creature's turn. Rennak the Loyal regains spent legendary actions at the start of its turn. 
:
**Planar Tear** (2 Legendary Actions): Rennak The Loyal ignites his Hell Claws to slice a tear in the very fabric of reality, creating a Hell Portal. The Portal lasts for 1 minute and any creature who is within 10ft of the portal takes 14 (4d6) fire damage and must roll a DC 14 Dexterity saving throw or be lit aflame by **Hellfire.** This fire cannot be extinguished, and will continue to burn for 5 (1d10) hours. 
:
**Multiattack** (1 Legendary Action): Rennak The Loyal makes three attacks. 1 with his **Hell Claws**, 1 with his **Wicked Blade** and 1 with his **Tail Pierce**. 
:
**Legendary Patience** (2 Legendary Actions): Rennak The Loyal can forgo his turn to gain the use of 3 additional Legendary Actions on his following turn. If Rennak The Loyal takes damage before his next turn, he must make a Concentration Check to maintain his patience. For each failure, Rennak The Loyal loses a Legendary Action. If no Legendary Actions remain, Rennak The Loyal loses a Legendary Resistance, instead. 
:
**Tyrant's Blessing** (6 Legendary Actions): Rennak The Loyal regains the use of his **Breath Weapon** and instantly uses it. This damage cannot be resisted, mitigated or stopped. If a creature is reduced to half of their Max HP below 0, the creature is ***Disintegrated*** along with all of their belongings, magic and non-magical.



}}

