:
***Frost-Fire Bow.*** _Ranged Weapon Attack:_ +18 to hit, range 150/600 ft., one target. _Hit:_ 16 (1d10 + 11) piercing damage. Hit or miss, the target must make a DC 15 Dexterity saving throw or take 21 (6d6) Cold damage. The FrostFire Bow was forged in the depths of the Hells, combining Hell-Flame and Cauterizing-Cold. If a target is Immune or Resistant to Fire or Cold Damage, the Damage of the Frost-Fire Bow deals Vulnerable Damage of the opposite Damage type.

### Legendary Actions
***Merciliess Strikes*** Frislyc makes 4 attacks with his Frost-Fire Bow. If he misses an attack, he can instead expend a hit die, and reroll the attack.
