### Slycur, Heir of The Many-Mawed

![homebrew mug](https://github.com/PhantomDesk74/Homebrewery_Assets/blob/main/CharacterArt/Slycur%20Heir%20of%20the%20Many-Mawed.png?raw=true) {position:absolute,top:250px,right:265px,width:300px}
