<!-- Back Cover -->

{{backCover}}

# Weave Together
# Your Destiny

The Lands of Fal'doren are vast. From the Frozen wates of the Slab, to the rolling dunes of the Tarrel Desert, adventure awaits in all corners of the world. Throughout this setting you will find many paths to unimaginable strengths, deep stories, and rich histories.
:
Embark on a thrilling journey across a vast and varied world, where magic and mystery await you at every turn. Encounter strange creatures and ancient secrets, and forge your own destiny with your choices. The world is yours to shape and explore.
:
Create your own character and enter a realm of endless possibilities, where you can even unlock untold power in Hero Classes! This new end-game feature allows even more depth to unlock with your character, and even more story to emerge.
___

For use with Dungeons & Dragons 5e (Pre-2024 Ruleset) and Homebrew Rules. Play the best game of your life!

![background image](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PhantomDesk74/Homebrewery_Assets/refs/heads/main/BookArt/Fractured%20Destiny%20Cover%20No%20Text.png){position:absolute,bottom:0,left:0,height:100%}

